snippet.title: Comic 5trike - Alpha - May Build Test
snippet.description:
Checkout the latest in enemies in the game that chase you down and try to give you an explosive hug.

Follow the game on Reddit!
https://www.reddit.com/r/Comic5trikeGame/

Watch the development on Twitch!
https://www.twitch.tv/comic5trike_dev

Support the game on Patreon!
https://www.patreon.com/Comic5trike

Comic 5trike is a game being developed for the PC, still in Alpha and with much to be added it is slowly taking form into what can be a hopefully great game!

Try it out at this link!
https://www.dropbox.com/s/n0x818c3h77r47n/Build.zip?dl=1
